HEADWORD: paramagnet
<hw>par`a*mag"net</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A substance exhibiting
<er>paramagnetism</er>, i.e. a substance whose magnetization is
proportional to the strength of the magnetic field applied to
it.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Paramagnetic</ent>⟦br⟧
